I"ç<h1 id="stash">Stash</h1>

<div class="infobox box text-center">
    <p style="text-align:center;"><img src="../../assets/images/items/stashbox.png" alt="Stashbox" /></p>
    <recipe>stash</recipe>
</div>
<p><br /></p>

<p>The stash lets a player deposit items that they want to be picked up by a <a href="../../source/workers/courier">Courier</a> to take to the <a href="../../source/buildings/warehouse">Warehouse</a>.</p>

<p>The stash can be crafted at the <a href="../../source/buildings/sawmill">Sawmill</a> or by the player.
<br /></p>

<h2 id="using-the-stash">Using the Stash</h2>

<p>To use the stash, right-click on it to bring up the inventory, which works like a chest. Put items in the stash and a Courier will pick them up.</p>
